Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:04.52,0:00:07.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看過上個月久留美的健康資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:07.76,0:00:10.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卻沒發現類似這次的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:10.86,0:00:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全健康
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.46,0:00:13.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果不是生病，那就是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.43,0:00:15.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,超能力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然在一陣光之中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.07,0:00:22.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,呼喚出天使
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.64,0:00:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了超能力，別無它想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.18,0:00:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我…沒那種能力的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:31.38,0:00:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道，只是開個玩笑而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:33.72,0:00:35.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要對身體沒害的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:36.02,0:00:37.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不用太在意了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:39.09,0:00:41.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…感覺很不舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.59,0:00:43.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,召喚出天使的少女
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:44.40,0:00:47.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在研究題目來講也許會很有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:47.87,0:00:49.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也要替我想想啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.33,0:00:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊~這胸圍的數字
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.01,0:00:56.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然比去年還要大了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.34,0:00:59.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡玲加，不要亂看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:59.68,0:01:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太氣人了，我和去年一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:01.98,0:01:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全沒有變過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.25,0:01:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳雖然這樣講…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.95,0:01:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也不用那麼灰心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:07.72,0:01:09.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳還是處於成長期啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.39,0:01:11.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳根本沒資格講我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.62,0:01:14.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不能原諒，久留美這白癡白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.09,0:01:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,(ANGEL SMILE)
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:26.70,0:01:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去參加社團了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.81,0:01:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果今天可以見到他的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:29.64,0:01:30.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要做告白啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.84,0:01:32.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 妳敢講出來嗎？\N- 也許…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是才見第二次面就告白
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.65,0:01:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們不覺得太快了一點嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:37.25,0:01:38.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得妳還是放棄比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:39.28,0:01:42.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，妳們這算是替我加油嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.75,0:01:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然有在替妳加油啊，加油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.59,0:01:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳既然有那種引人的身材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:48.83,0:01:51.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那條裙子可否再短一點呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.00,0:01:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是…是嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:54.30,0:01:58.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 卡玲加！\N- 明白的講出自己心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:58.24,0:01:59.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才是最重要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.64,0:02:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是說明要他抱妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.61,0:02:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.24,0:02:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,希望他…抱我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.91,0:02:07.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別聽卡玲加亂講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.31,0:02:09.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,直接表示自己的心意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.85,0:02:11.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,『我喜歡你』，『請和我交往』
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.75,0:02:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣講就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:15.05,0:02:15.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:17.02,0:02:18.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請和我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.56,0:02:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.26,0:02:22.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請和我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.66,0:02:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡你…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.03,0:02:28.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯，我知道了，我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.44,0:02:40.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那樣叫做手腳同步嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:41.78,0:02:43.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會很順利的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.25,0:02:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最好別那麼順利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.38,0:02:46.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.49,0:02:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 她又那麼講了\N- 耶雪麗亞…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.50,0:03:01.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們去偷看久留美的社團活動吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以那樣做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:04.07,0:03:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳不想知道她怎麼做告白嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:06.54,0:03:08.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沙希也很有興趣吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:09.17,0:03:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然有，但是不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.81,0:03:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，妳這個人真正直
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:14.08,0:03:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，卡玲加，陪我去買東西吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.32,0:03:19.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等久留美回來，我們要祝賀她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.08,0:03:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果失敗了，就是安慰派對了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.82,0:03:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣講
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.26,0:03:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶雪麗亞，妳呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:27.73,0:03:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我還有東西要查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.33,0:03:30.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託妳看家了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:32.76,0:03:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:40.74,0:03:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使－Holder
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.98,0:03:46.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這兩個是碰巧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.88,0:03:48.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還是必然的呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.08,0:03:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想和大家一起得到幸福…嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.11,0:04:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以偷吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.64,0:04:19.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要等久留美回來之後才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.31,0:04:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:20.81,0:04:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳們覺不覺得久留美有點遲？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.55,0:04:25.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:26.18,0:04:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,社團活動早就已經結束了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.22,0:04:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也許是太順利了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.42,0:04:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以和對方做了非常的事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:32.69,0:04:34.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳…妳亂說什麼！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.56,0:04:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的，妳不用那麼興奮啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.26,0:04:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊，難不成沙希沒有經驗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.07,0:04:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎麼可能有呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.94,0:04:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.31,0:04:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀呀，妳們真是純真少女啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.61,0:04:53.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,卡玲加，妳有經驗嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:58.12,0:04:58.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.36,0:05:12.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.03,0:05:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看樣子好像失敗了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.14,0:05:20.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊…那…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.94,0:05:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，妳…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.19,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,失敗了嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.46,0:05:45.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎樣？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.93,0:05:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶雪麗亞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:49.93,0:05:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說願意和我交往
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.40,0:05:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.74,0:05:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.94,0:05:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,突然哭了出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:55.37,0:05:56.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,害人以為妳失敗了呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別嚇人啊，討厭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.31,0:06:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,事情不是很順利嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.98,0:06:05.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼還要哭呢？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.48,0:06:07.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他不是願意和妳交往嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.52,0:06:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有一個星期而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.12,0:06:13.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個星期？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.59,0:06:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼意思？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.96,0:06:20.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道人先生一個星期後就要離開了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.33,0:06:22.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要到很遠的地方去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.23,0:06:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他說不能再見面了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.17,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今天跟他告白的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.11,0:06:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道道人先生對我也有意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.78,0:06:35.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我非常的高興
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.08,0:06:40.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是，一個星期後就要分開…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.15,0:06:45.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…\N這種事，我不想
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.73,0:06:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,- 我們乾杯吧\N- 卡玲加？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.10,0:07:00.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美有了男朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:01.14,0:07:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這不是很值得高興的事情嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.17,0:07:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是那個人…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.61,0:07:06.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個人…道人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.81,0:07:08.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也是喜歡久留美的吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.11,0:07:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有比這樣更加幸福的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.48,0:07:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算只有一個星期也無所謂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.95,0:07:15.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.75,0:07:17.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們一起製造許多的美好回憶吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.12,0:07:19.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之後再哭也不遲啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.02,0:07:20.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.39,0:07:24.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為…他是妳喜歡的人吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.50,0:07:26.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.76,0:07:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳哭的話，道人會難過的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.00,0:07:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳不想讓他難過吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對吧，久留美？回答我！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.32,0:07:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想讓他難過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.13,0:07:56.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.43,0:07:57.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.13,0:08:00.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就太對不起道人先生了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.10,0:08:01.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.03,0:08:05.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝妳，卡玲加
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.10,0:08:07.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會再哭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.97,0:08:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，妳的臉全部都是淚水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.68,0:08:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去洗個臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.31,0:08:12.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:14.08,0:08:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是會給人找麻煩  真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.86,0:08:25.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不可以哭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:26.66,0:08:27.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要笑才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.23,0:08:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我已經很幸福了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.96,0:08:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家都很關心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.63,0:08:37.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為我喜歡道人先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:22.01,0:09:22.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.75,0:09:25.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我的愛越深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:26.05,0:09:27.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使就會出現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:28.22,0:09:30.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,正如喜歡道人先生的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.32,0:09:31.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼閃耀著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:32.56,0:09:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天使就會顯現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.29,0:09:37.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為天使代表祝福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.63,0:09:39.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定不會有問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.33,0:09:42.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定可以得到幸福的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.94,0:09:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果說…因為愛能讓天使降臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.38,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個我相信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.38,0:09:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,奇蹟會…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.75,0:10:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,耶雪麗亞，愛哭的久留美
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.95,0:10:01.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還在裡面洗臉嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:02.19,0:10:02.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.95,0:10:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美，快點啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.96,0:10:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我要全部吃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.39,0:10:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會留給妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.80,0:10:17.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我走了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,終於等到第一次約會了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.91,0:10:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她應該沒事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.11,0:10:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久留美她…一定沒事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.55,0:10:32.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,日子就這樣過了一個星期
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.32,0:10:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:41.26,0:10:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去送他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.19,0:10:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,道人先生…剛才離開這裡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.44,0:10:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那一天，說過不再哭的久留美…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.01,0:10:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭了一整晚
